claim.claim-text:
An electronic device assembly comprising:
a master device comprising a radio frequency (RF) connecting module, the RF connecting module comprising a plurality of master RF modules, each master RF module comprising one type of master interface; and
a plurality of slave devices, each slave device comprising a slave RF module, and the slave RF module comprising different types of slave interfaces;
wherein the number of types of master interfaces of the master device are greater than or equal to the number of types of slave interfaces of the plurality of slave devices;
each master interface is connected to a corresponding slave interface via a wireless connection; and
each master interface has the same wireless format and the same signal format as the slave interface corresponding thereto.
